# Deployed Express API (no trailing slash). When set, EVERY request goes here (not the Vite proxy).
# If Admin → Ads or Packages returns 404, either:
#   (1) Redeploy Render with the latest server code, or
#   (2) Comment out VITE_API_URL so /api is proxied to your machine (run `npm run dev` in server/).
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-api.onrender.com

# Where Vite sends /api and /uploads when VITE_API_URL is unset (local backend).
# VITE_DEV_PROXY_TARGET=http://localhost:5000

# Verify production: GET https://your-api.onrender.com/api/health
# Should include "features":{"adminAds":true,...}. If only {"ok":true}, the old server is still deployed.
